Quickstrike:




"He's new 'round here." Quickstrike replied. "He's uh clone of Megatron's 
original bots that came wit' 'im on th' Darkside, his old ship. They say 
that he died falling inta th' lava. It was uh real rugged ship. Had t' move 
around some places on uh platform. Ah choose this guy 'cause he was uh 
flier." He sighed. "Ah wonder when boss-bot an th' others are comin' back."

Just then, Terrorsaur took flight through the cave, swooping down close 
enough to snap his long beak at Sinester, and fly to his stalactmite mound.
